#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Sissejuhatus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ark; is a program for viewing, extracting, creating and modifying archives. "
"&ark; can handle various archive formats such as <command>tar</command>, "
"<command>gzip</command>, <command>bzip2</command>, <command>zip</command>, "
"<command>rar</command>, <command>7zip</command>, <command>xz</command>, "
"<command>rpm</command>, <command>cab</command>, <command>deb</command>, "
"<command>xar</command> and <command>AppImage</command> (support for certain "
"archive formats depends on the appropriate command-line programs being "
"installed)."
msgstr ""
"&ark; on rakendus mitmesuguste arhiivivormingute vaatamiseks. "
"lahtipakkimiseks, loomiseks ja muutmiseks. Rakendus suudab toime tulla "
"erinevate vormingutega, näiteks <command>tar</command>, <command>gzip</"
"command>, <command>bzip2</command>, <command>zip</command>, <command>rar</"
"command>, <command>7zip</command>, <command>xz</command>, <command>rpm</"
"command>, <command>cab</command>, <command>deb</command>, <command>xar</"
"command> ja <command>AppImage</command> (konkreetse arhiivivormingu toetus "
"sõltub sellest, kas paigaldatud on vastav käsureaprogramm)."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "&ark;'s main window"
msgstr "&ark;i peaaken"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In order to successfully use &ark;, you need KDE Frameworks 5. The library "
"libarchive version 3.1 or above is needed to handle most archive types, "
"including tar, compressed tar, rpm, deb and cab archives. To handle other "
"file formats, you need the appropriate command line programs, such as "
"<command>zipinfo</command>, <command>zip</command>, <command>unzip</"
"command>, <command>rar</command>, <command>unrar</command>, <command>7z</"
"command>, <command>lsar</command>, <command>unar</command> and "
"<command>lrzip</command>."
msgstr ""
"&ark;i edukaks kasutamiseks on vajalik KDE Frameworks 5.  Teegi libarchive "
"versioon 3.1 või uuem on vajalik enamiku arhiivitüüpide käitlemiseks, "
"sealhulgas tar-, tihendatud tar-, rpm-, deb- ja cab-arhiivid. Teiste "
"failivormingute tarbeks on vajalikud vastavad käsureaprogrammid, näiteks "
"<command>zipinfo</command>, <command>zip</command>, <command>unzip</"
"command>, <command>rar</command>, <command>unrar</command>, <command>7z</"
"command>, <command>lsar</command>, <command>unar</command> ja "
"<command>lrzip</command>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &ark;"
msgstr "&ark;i kasutamine"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opening Archives"
msgstr "Arhiivide avamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To open an archive in &ark;, choose <guimenuitem>Open...</guimenuitem> "
"(<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo>) from the "
"<guimenu>Archive</guimenu> menu. You can also open archive files by dragging "
"and dropping from &dolphin;. Archive files should be associated with &ark;, "
"so you can also <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click a file in &dolphin; "
"and select <guimenuitem>Open with &ark;</guimenuitem> to open it or select "
"an extract action for this file."
msgstr ""
"Arhiivi avamiseks &ark;is vali menüüst <guimenu>Arhiiv</guimenu> käsk "
"<guimenuitem>Ava...</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo>). Arhiivi saab avada ka seda &dolphin;ist "
"kohale lohistades. Arhiivifaile saab seostada &ark;iga, mille järel on "
"võimalik neil &dolphin;is hiire <mousebutton>parema</mousebutton> nupuga "
"klõpsata ja valida nende <guimenuitem>avamine &ark;</guimenuitem>is või "
"lahtipakkimine."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have enabled the information panel in the <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"menu additional information about the selected folders or files in the "
"archive is displayed."
msgstr ""
"Kui oled <guimenu>seadistuste</guimenu>menüüs sisse lülitanud teabepaneelide "
"näitamise, siis näidatakse lisateavet arhiivi valitud kataloogide või "
"failide kohta."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid "Archive Operations"
msgstr "Arhiivitoimingud"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Various operations can be performed for an opened archive by using the "
"<guimenu>Archive</guimenu> menu. For example, you can save the archive with "
"a different name using <guimenuitem>Save As...</guimenuitem>. Archive "
"properties such as type, size and MD5 hash can be viewed using the "
"<guimenuitem>Properties</guimenuitem> item."
msgstr ""
"Avatud arhiiviga saab mitmesuguseid toiminguid ette võtta menüü "
"<guimenu>Arhiiv</guimenu> vahendusel. Näiteks võib arhiivi salvestada teise "
"nimega käsu <guimenuitem>Salvesta kui ...</guimenuitem> abil. Käsuga "
"<guimenuitem>Omadused</guimenuitem> saab aga näha arhiivi omadusi, näiteks "
"tüüpi, suurust ja MD5 räsi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ark; has the ability to test archives for integrity. This functionality is "
"currently available for <command>zip</command>, <command>rar</command> and "
"<command>7z</command> archives. The test action can be found in the "
"<guimenu>Archive</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"&ark; võib kontrollida arhiivi terviklikkust. Praegu saab seda teha "
"<command>zip</command>-, <command>rar</command>- ja <command>7z</command>-"
"arhiivide korral. Testimiskäsu leiab menüüst <guimenu>Arhiiv</guimenu>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid "Archive Comments"
msgstr "Arhiivi kommentaarid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ark; can handle comments embedded in <literal role=\"extension\">zip</"
"literal> and <literal role=\"extension\">rar</literal> archives."
msgstr ""
"&ark; suudab toime tulla kommentaaridega, mis on põimitud <literal role="
"\"extension\">zip</literal> ja <literal role=\"extension\">rar</literal>-"
"arhiividesse."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Comments embedded in <literal role=\"extension\">zip</literal> archives are "
"automatically displayed."
msgstr ""
"Kommentaare, mis on põimitud <literal role=\"extension\">zip</literal>-"
"arhiivi, näidatakse automaatselt."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using <literal role=\"extension\">rar</literal> archives you can modify a "
"comment with the actions <guimenuitem>Add Comment</guimenuitem> or "
"<guimenuitem>Edit comment</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo>) from the <guimenu>Archive</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"<literal role=\"extension\">rar</literal>-arhiivi korral saab "
"kommentaaridega üht-teist ette võtta käskude <guimenuitem>Lisa kommentaar</"
"guimenuitem> ja <guimenuitem>Muuda kommentaari</guimenuitem> (<keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo>) varal, mille leiab "
"menüüst <guimenu>Arhiiv</guimenu>."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing a comment"
msgstr "Kommentaari muutmine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The comment menu item is enabled only for <literal role=\"extension\">rar</"
"literal> archives."
msgstr ""
"Kommentaariga seotud menüükirje on aktiivne ainult <literal role=\"extension"
"\">rar</literal>-arhiivi korral."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To remove a comment from a <literal role=\"extension\">rar</literal> archive "
"delete the text in the comment window."
msgstr ""
"Kommentaari eemaldamiseks <literal role=\"extension\">rar</literal>-"
"arhiivist kustuta kommentaariaknas tekst."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "Working with Files"
msgstr "Töö failidega"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once an archive has been opened, you can perform various operations on the "
"files inside the archive. By selecting a file and using the <guimenu>File</"
"guimenu> menu, you can choose different operations to perform:"
msgstr ""
"Kui arhiiv on avatud, võib selles leiduvate failidega ette võtta "
"mitmesuguseid asju. Faili valides ja kasutades menüüd <guimenu>Fail</"
"guimenu> saab ette võtta järgmist:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Preview</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo>) will open the file with &ark;'s internal "
"viewer. This is a fast read-only viewer, but does not support all file types."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Eelvaatlus</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo>) avab faili &ark;i sisemises näitajas. See on "
"kiire kirjutuskaitstud näitaja, aga see ei toeta kõiki failitüüpe."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Open</guimenuitem> will open the file in the associated "
"application for that file type."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Ava</guimenuitem> avab faili selle failitüübiga seostatud "
"rakenduses."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Open With...</guimenuitem> allows you to choose which "
"application to open the file with."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Ava rakendusega...</guimenuitem> võimaldab valida, millise "
"rakendusega fail avada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Rename</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo>) This action allows to change names of both "
"files and folders. As in the Dolphin file manager, this action can be called "
"via a shortcut and renaming is done via inline editing. There are also "
"filename checks provided, which prevent usage of invalid characters such as "
"<userinput>/</userinput>, <userinput>.</userinput> and <userinput>..</"
"userinput> in filenames."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Muuda nime</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo>): see võimaldab muuta nii failide kui ka "
"kataloogide nime. Sarnaselt failihaldurile Dolphin saab toimingut esile "
"kutsuda kiirklahviga ning nime muuta ka kohe sisestusreal kirjutades. "
"Failinime kontrollitakse, mis välistab nimes lubamatute märkide kasutamise "
"(näiteks <userinput>/</userinput>, <userinput>.</userinput> ja <userinput>.."
"</userinput>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Delete</guimenuitem> (<keycap>Del</keycap>) will remove the "
"currently selected file(s) from the archive. Note that this action is "
"undoable."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Kustuta</guimenuitem> (<keycap>Del</keycap>) eemaldab arhiivist "
"parajasti valitud faili(d). Pane tähele, et seda käsku ei saa tagasi võtta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Extract</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo>) opens a submenu with previously accessed "
"folders, and you can choose to quickly extract into any of these or browse "
"to a non-listed folder. See the next section for more details on extraction."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Lahtipakkimine</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo>) avab alammenüü varem kasutatud kataloogidega, "
"mille seast saab valida selle, kuhu lahti pakkida. Samuti saab seal sirvida "
"teisi katalooge, et valida lahtipakkimiseks mõni varem kasutamata kataloog. "
"Täpsemalt kõneldakse lahtipakkimisest tagapool."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</"
"keycap></keycombo>) / <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo>) / <guimenuitem>Paste</"
"guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></"
"keycombo>): As in typical file managers, moving, pasting and copying are "
"provided. Users can move or copy files from different folders (which are "
"expandable in the tree view) and paste them to the same destination at once. "
"A folder can be copied into itself, but can not be moved. There are also "
"checks for conflicting filenames: You won't be able to copy or move files "
"into a folder that has entries with the same names - that could lead to data "
"loss."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Lõika</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo>) / <guimenuitem>Kopeeri</guimenuitem> "
"(<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo>) / "
"<guimenuitem>Aseta</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo>): bagu tüüpilises failihalduris, pakutakse "
"liigutamise, asetamise ja kopeerimise võimalust. Kasutaja saab liigutada või "
"kopeerida faile eri kataloogidest (mida saab puuvaates laiendada) ja asetada "
"neid korraga ühte sihtkohta. Kataloogi saab ka iseendasse kopeerida, aga "
"mitte liigutada. Samuti kontrollitakse failinime konflikte: faile ei saa saa "
"liigutada ega kopeerida kataloogi, kus juba on sama nimega kirjed, sest see "
"võiks kaasa tuua andmekao."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Add Files</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo>) This action can be used to add files at any "
"location within the archive. If you select a folder and use this action, "
"files will be added to the selected folder. Otherwise, the new files will be "
"added to the root of the archive."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Lisa faile</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo>): selle käsuga saab lisada faile arhiivi mis "
"tahes asukohta. Kui valid kataloogi ja kasutad seda käsku, lisatakse failid "
"valitud kataloogi. Vastasel juhul lisatakse uued failid arhiivi "
"juurkataloogi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing Files"
msgstr "Failide muutmine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you edit and save a file which you opened using <guimenuitem>Open</"
"guimenuitem> or <guimenuitem>Open With...</guimenuitem>, Ark will ask you if "
"you want to update the file in the archive. If you answer Yes, the archive "
"will be updated with the saved file."
msgstr ""
"Kui muudad ja salvestad faili, mille oled avanud käsuga <guimenuitem>Ava</"
"guimenuitem> või <guimenuitem>Ava rakendusega...</guimenuitem>, küsib Ark, "
"kas uuendada faili ka arhiivis. Kui vastad jaatavalt, uuendataksegi arhiivi "
"salvestatud failiga."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid "Extracting Files"
msgstr "Failide lahtipakkimine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once an archive has been opened in &ark;, it can be extracted. This can be "
"done by selecting <guisubmenu>Extract</guisubmenu> from the <guimenu>File</"
"guimenu> menu. This opens a submenu with previously accessed folders, and "
"you can choose to quickly extract into any of these. Alternatively, select "
"the submenu item <guisubmenu>Extract To...</guisubmenu> to open the "
"<guilabel>Extract</guilabel> dialog, where you can set various options that "
"affect the extraction. See below for information on the available options in "
"the Extract dialog."
msgstr ""
"Kui arhiiv on &ark;is avatud, saab selle ka lahti pakkida. Failide "
"lahtipakkimiseks vali menüüst <guimenu>Fail</guimenu> alammenüü "
"<guisubmenu>Lahtipakkimine</guisubmenu>. See avab varem kasutatud "
"kataloogide nimekirja, kus saab valida, kuhu lahtipakkimine ette võtta. "
"Teine võimalus on valida alammenüüst <guisubmenu>Paki lahti...</guisubmenu>, "
"mis avab dialoogi <guilabel>Lahtipakkimine</guilabel>, kus saab paika panna "
"mitmesuguseid lahtipakkimist mõjutavaid valikuid. Täpsemalt kõneldakse selle "
"dialoogi valikutest tagapool."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also use the <guibutton>Extract</guibutton> button in the toolbar to "
"access the same extraction options."
msgstr ""
"Samasuguste lahtipakkimisvalikute kasutamiseks võib klõpsata ka "
"tööriistaribal nuppu <guibutton>Paki lahti</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To extract the entire archive, you can select <guisubmenu>Extract All</"
"guisubmenu> from the <guimenu>Archive</guimenu> menu. This action "
"unconditionally extracts all files in the archive."
msgstr ""
"Kogu arhiivi lahtipakkimiseks võib valida menüüst <guimenu>Arhiiv</guimenu> "
"käsu <guisubmenu>Paki kõik lahti</guisubmenu>. Selle käsu järel pakitakse "
"tingimusteta lahti kõik arhiivi failid."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to extract files and folders by simply dragging them with the "
"mouse to a folder in &dolphin;."
msgstr ""
"Faile ja katalooge saab lahti pakkida neid ka lihtsalt hiirega &dolphin;is "
"kataloogi lohistades."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note: Extracting files from an archive does not change the archive and its "
"contents."
msgstr ""
"Märkus: failide lahtipakkimine arhiivist ei muuda arhiivi ega selle sisu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:250
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Extract dialog"
msgstr "Lahtipakkimisdialoog"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Extract</guilabel> dialog allows you to choose where the files "
"will be extracted to. The default location is the folder the archive is in. "
"The dialog can also be opened by pressing <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Dialoog <guilabel>Lahtipakkimine</guilabel> võimaldab valida, kuhu failid "
"lahti pakitakse. Vaikimisi on asukohaks kataloog, milles arhiiv asub. "
"Dialoogi saab avada ka kiirklahviga <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:261
#, no-c-format
msgid "&ark;'s Extract dialog"
msgstr "&ark;i lahtipakkimisdialoog"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can specify to extract the files into a subfolder. The default name of "
"this subfolder is the archive name without the filename extension, but you "
"can edit it to your needs. If you want to preserve paths when extracting, "
"select the <guilabel>Preserve paths when extracting</guilabel> option. You "
"may also choose to open the destination folder in &dolphin; or close &ark; "
"once the extraction is complete."
msgstr ""
"Failid võib lahti pakkida ka alamkataloogi. Vaikimisi antakse "
"alamkataloogile nimeks arhiivi nimi ilma laiendita, kuid seda võib "
"loomulikult muuta. Kui soovid säilitada lahtipakkimisel asukohad, tuleks "
"märkida <guilabel>Lahtipakkimisel säilitatakse asukohad</guilabel>. Samuti "
"saab määrata, et sihtkataloog avatakse &dolphin;is, või et &ark; suletakse, "
"kui lahtipakkimine on tehtud."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If one or more files in the archive list are highlighted, you can also "
"select which files to extract:"
msgstr ""
"Kui arhiivi nimekirjas on mõni fail esile tõstetud, saab ka valida, millised "
"failid lahti pakkida:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Selected files only</guilabel> extracts only the files which have "
"been selected."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Ainult valitud failid</guilabel> pakib lahti ainult valitud failid."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>All files</guilabel> extracts the entire contents of the archive."
msgstr "<guilabel>Kõik failid</guilabel> pakib lahti kogu arhiivi sisu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating Archives and Adding Files"
msgstr "Arhiivide loomine ja failide lisamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create a new archive in &ark;, choose <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem> "
"(<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo>) from the "
"<guimenu>Archive</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Uue arhiivi loomiseks &ark;is vali menüüst <guimenu>Arhiiv</guimenu> käsk "
"<guimenuitem>Uus</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</"
"keycap></keycombo>)."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create an archive"
msgstr "Arhiivi loomine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:303
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can then type the name of the archive, with the appropriate extension "
"(<literal role=\"extension\">tar.gz</literal>, <literal role=\"extension"
"\">zip</literal>, <literal role=\"extension\">7z</literal>, &etc;) or select "
"a supported format in the <guilabel>Filter</guilabel> combo box and check "
"the <guilabel>Automatically add <replaceable>filename extension</"
"replaceable></guilabel> option."
msgstr ""
"Seejärel saad kirjutada arhiivi nime koos sobiva laiendiga (<literal role="
"\"extension\">tar.gz</literal>, <literal role=\"extension\">zip</literal>, "
"<literal role=\"extension\">7z</literal> &etc;) või valida mõne toetatud "
"vormingu liitkastis <guilabel>Filter</guilabel> ja märkida ära ruudukese "
"<guilabel><replaceable>Failinime laiendi</replaceable> automaatne lisamine</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To add files or folders to the new archive, choose <guimenuitem>Add Files..."
"</guimenuitem> from the <guimenu>Archive</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Failide või kataloogide lisamiseks uude arhiivi vali menüüst "
"<guimenu>Arhiiv</guimenu> käsk <guimenuitem>Lisa faile...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:312
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An alternative way to add files to an archive is to drag one or more files "
"from e.g. &dolphin; into the main &ark; window, and it will be added to the "
"current archive. Note that files added in this way will always be added to "
"the root directory of the archive."
msgstr ""
"Teine viis faile arhiivi lisada on lohistada fail või failid näiteks "
"&dolphin;ist &ark;i peaaknasse ning need lisataksegi parajasti avatud "
"arhiivi. Pane tähele, et sel moel lisatud failid lisatakse alati arhiivi "
"juurkataloogi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additional options are presented in collapsible groups at the bottom of the "
"dialog."
msgstr "Lisavõimalusi näeb dialoog allosas kokkukerivates rühmades."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compression"
msgstr "Pakkimine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A higher value generates smaller archives, but results in longer compression "
"and decompression times. The default compression level proposed by &ark; is "
"usually a good compromise between size and (de)compression speed. For most "
"formats the minimum compression level is equivalent to just storing the "
"files, &ie; applying no compression."
msgstr ""
"Suurem väärtus loob väiksemad arhiivid, aga pakkimine ja lahtipakkimine "
"võtab kauem aega. &ark;i pakutav vaikimisi pakkimise tase on tavaliselt "
"mõistlik kompromiss suuruse ja (lahti)pakkimise kiiruse vahel. Enamiku "
"vormingute puhul võrdub minimaalne pakkimise tase lihtsalt faili "
"salvestamisega, s.t. igasuguse pakkimise puudumisega."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:326
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For <literal role=\"extension\">rar</literal>, <literal role=\"extension"
"\">7z</literal> and <literal role=\"extension\">zip</literal> archives you "
"can select between different compression methods."
msgstr ""
"<literal role=\"extension\">rar</literal>, <literal role=\"extension\">7z</"
"literal> ja <literal role=\"extension\">zip</literal>-arhiivide korral saab "
"valida mitme tihendusviisi vahel."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that using compression methods other than the pre-selected defaults may "
"limit compatibility with file archivers. For example, opening <literal role="
"\"extension\">zip</literal> archives with compression methods other than "
"<quote>Deflate</quote> requires newer archiving software."
msgstr ""
"Pane tähele, et mõne muu kui vaikimisi pakutava tihendusviisi kasutamine "
"võib piirata ühilduvust muude arhiiviprogrammidega. Näiteks <literal role="
"\"extension\">zip</literal>-arhiivide avamine mõne muu tihendusviisiga kui "
"<quote>Deflate</quote> nõuab päris uut arhiveerimistarkvara."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:335
#, no-c-format
msgid "Password Protection"
msgstr "Paroolikaitse"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you create a <literal role=\"extension\">zip</literal>, <literal role="
"\"extension\">rar</literal>, <literal role=\"extension\">7zip</literal> and "
"<literal role=\"extension\">jar</literal> archive you can protect it with a "
"password. Currently, only the <literal role=\"extension\">zip</literal> "
"format supports multiple encryption methods. For other formats that support "
"only one encryption method, the method is shown in the drop down box."
msgstr ""
"Kui lood <literal role=\"extension\">zip</literal>-, <literal role="
"\"extension\">rar</literal>-, <literal role=\"extension\">7zip</literal>- "
"või <literal role=\"extension\">jar</literal>-arhiivi, võid selle kaitsta "
"parooliga. Praegu toetab ainult <literal role=\"extension\">zip</literal>-"
"vorming mitut krüptimisviisi. Teiste vormingute korral, mis toetavad ainult "
"üht krüptimisviisi, näidatakse seda rippmenüüs."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:342
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Other encryption methods than the default <guilabel>ZipCrypto</guilabel> "
"might not be supported by all file archivers."
msgstr ""
"Sugugi kõik arhiveerimisprogrammid ei pruugi toetada teisi krüptimisviise "
"peale vaikimisi meetodi <guilabel>ZipCrypto</guilabel>."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a password protected archive"
msgstr "Parooliga kaitstud arhiivi loomine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:354
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose whether to require the password before showing the list of files. "
"This is called header encryption and is available only with the <literal "
"role=\"extension\">rar</literal> and <literal role=\"extension\">7zip</"
"literal> formats. Header encryption is enabled by default (when available), "
"in order to offer the maximum protection for novice users."
msgstr ""
"Vali, kas parooli küsitakse enne failide nimekirja näitamist. Viimast "
"nimetatakse päise krüptimiseks ja seda saab kasutada ainult <literal role="
"\"extension\">rar</literal> ja <literal role=\"extension\">7zip</literal> "
"vormingu korral. Väiksemate kogemustega kasutajate maksimaalseks kaitsmiseks "
"on päise krüptimine (kui see on muidugi üldse võimalik) vaikimisi sisse "
"lülitatud."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid "Multi-volume Archive"
msgstr "Mitmeköiteline arhiiv"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:363
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With the <literal role=\"extension\">zip</literal>, <literal role=\"extension"
"\">rar</literal> and <literal role=\"extension\">7z</literal> formats you "
"can create multi-volume archives, also known as multi-part or split archives."
msgstr ""
"Kui lood <literal role=\"extension\">zip</literal>-, <literal role="
"\"extension\">rar</literal>- või <literal role=\"extension\">7zip</literal>-"
"arhiivi, saad selle luua ka mitmeköitelise ehk mitmeosalise ehk tükeldatud "
"arhiivina."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A multi-volume archive is one big compressed archive split into several "
"files. This feature is useful if the maximum file size is limited, &eg; by "
"the capacity of a storage medium or the maximal size of an email with "
"attachments."
msgstr ""
"Mitmeköiteline arhiiv kujutab endast üht suurt tihendatud arhiivi, mis on "
"tükeldatud mitmeks failiks. See võimalus on abiks, kui maksimaalne faili "
"suurus on piiratud (näiteks salvestusseadme mahuga või e-posti rakenduse "
"seatud piiranguga kirja manuse suurusele)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:369
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create a multi-volume archive, check the <guilabel>Create multi-volume "
"archive</guilabel> checkbox and set a maximum <guilabel>Volume size</"
"guilabel> in the dialog. Then add all files to the archive and &ark; will "
"automatically generate the required number of archive volumes. Depending on "
"the selected format the files have an extension with consecutively numbering "
"scheme &eg; <filename>xxx.7z.001</filename>, <filename>xxx.7z.002</filename> "
"or <filename>xxx.zip.001</filename>, <filename>xxx.zip.002</filename> or "
"<filename>xxx.part1.rar</filename>, <filename>xxx.part2.rar</filename> &etc;."
msgstr ""
"Mitmeköitelise arhiivi loomiseks märgi kastike <guilabel>Mitmeköitelise "
"arhiivi loomine</guilabel> ja pane dialoogis paika maksimaalne "
"<guilabel>köite suurus</guilabel>. Seejärel lisa kõik failid arhiivi ning "
"&ark; loob automaatselt vajaliku arvu arhiiviköiteid. Sõltuvalt valitud "
"vormingust on failidel laiend koos järjestikuste numbritega, &eg; "
"<filename>xxx.7z.001</filename>, <filename>xxx.7z.002</filename> or "
"<filename>xxx.zip.001</filename>, <filename>xxx.zip.002</filename> or "
"<filename>xxx.part1.rar</filename>, <filename>xxx.part2.rar</filename> &etc;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:376
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To extract a multi-volume archive, put all archive files into one folder and "
"open the file with the lowest extension number in &ark; and all other parts "
"of the split archive will be opened automatically."
msgstr ""
"Mitmeköitelise arhiivi lahtipakkimiseks paiguta kõik arhiivifailid ühte "
"kataloogi ning ava &ark;is fail, mille laiendis leidub number on kõige "
"väiksem. Selle peale peaksit automaatselt avanema ka kõik teised tükeldatud "
"arhiivi osad."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:386
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Using &ark; in the Filemanager"
msgid "Using &ark; in the File Manager"
msgstr "&ark;i kasutamine failihalduris"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:388
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Clicking with the &RMB; on an archive in a filemanager like &dolphin; "
#| "displays a context menu with an item <guimenuitem>Open with Ark</"
#| "guimenuitem>. The menu has these additional items to extract an archive "
#| "using &ark;:"
msgid ""
"Clicking with the &RMB; on an archive in a file manager like &dolphin; "
"displays a context menu with an item <guimenuitem>Extract</guimenuitem>. The "
"menu has these additional items to extract an archive using &ark;:"
msgstr ""
"Mõnes failihalduris, näiteks &dolphin;is, &HPNga; arhiivile klõpsates avaneb "
"kontekstimenüü kirjega <guimenuitem>Ava Arkis</guimenuitem>. Menüüs on "
"järgmised lisakirjed arhiivi lahtipakkimiseks &ark;i abil:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:395
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<guimenuitem>Extract Archive Here, Autodetect Subfolder</guimenuitem> "
#| "creates a subfolder in the folder with the archive and extracts the "
#| "folders and files into it."
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Extract here</guimenuitem> creates a subfolder in the folder "
"with the archive and extracts the folders and files into it. In case the "
"archive contains only one file or folder, no subfolder will be created."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Paki arhiiv siia lahti, tuvasta automaatselt alamkataloog</"
"guimenuitem> loob kataloogis alamkataloogi arhiiviga ning pakib kataloogid "
"ja failid sinna lahti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:400
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<guimenuitem>Extract Archive Here, Autodetect Subfolder</guimenuitem> "
#| "creates a subfolder in the folder with the archive and extracts the "
#| "folders and files into it."
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Extract here and delete archive</guimenuitem> creates a "
"subfolder in the folder with the archive, extracts the folders and files "
"into it and deletes the archive."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Paki arhiiv siia lahti, tuvasta automaatselt alamkataloog</"
"guimenuitem> loob kataloogis alamkataloogi arhiiviga ning pakib kataloogid "
"ja failid sinna lahti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:404
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<guimenuitem>Extract Archive To...</guimenuitem> opens the Extract dialog "
#| "where you can choose destination folder and various extraction options."
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Extract to…</guimenuitem> opens the Extract dialog where you "
"can choose the destination folder and various extraction options."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Paki arhiiv lahti asukohta...</guimenuitem> avab "
"lahtipakkimisdialoogi, kus saab valida sihtkataloogi ja mitmesuguseid "
"lahtipakkimise valikuid."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:408
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&dolphin;'s context menu for a selection of files and/or folders displays "
"these actions in the <guimenu>Compress</guimenu> submenu:"
msgstr ""
"&dolphin;i failide ja/või kataloogide valimise kontekstimenüüs leiab "
"alammenüüs <guimenu>Tihendamine</guimenu> järgmised toimingud:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:415
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<guimenuitem>Here (as TAR.GZ)</guimenuitem> or <guimenuitem>Here (as "
#| "ZIP)</guimenuitem> creates these archive types in the current folder."
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Compress to \"Archive.tar.gz\"</guimenuitem> and "
"<guimenuitem>Compress to \"Archive.zip\"</guimenuitem> creates these archive "
"types in the current folder."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Siia (TAR.GZ-arhiivina)</guimenuitem> või <guimenuitem>Siia "
"(ZIP-arhiivina)</guimenuitem> loob valitud arhiivitüübi aktiivsesse "
"kataloogi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:418
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Compress to...</guimenuitem> opens a dialog where you can "
"select folder, name and archive type."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Paki asukohta...</guimenuitem> avab dialoogi, kus saab valida "
"kataloogi, nime ja arhiivi tüübi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:425
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced Batch Mode"
msgstr "Täiustatud hulgirežiim"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:426
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ark; has an advanced batch mode to manage archives without launching a "
"graphical user interface. This mode allows you to extract or create archives "
"and add files to them."
msgstr ""
"&ark; pakub täiustatud hulgirežiimi arhiivide haldamiseks ilma graafilist "
"kasutajaliidest käivitamatagi. Selles režiimis on võimalik arhiive lahti "
"pakkida või luua ning neisse faile lisada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:429
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The batch mode is documented in <ulink url=\"man:/ark\">&ark;'s man page</"
"ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Hulgirežiimi kirjeldab lähemalt <ulink url=\"man:/ark\">&ark;i "
"manuaalilehekülg</ulink>."

